column16: Brian Dozier grounds into a double play, third baseman Kyle Seager to first baseman Logan Morrison.   Kurt Suzuki out at 3rd.
Chris Colabello lines out to right fielder Michael Saunders.
Kurt Suzuki singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Michael Saunders.
Josh Willingham out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Endy Chavez.   Trevor Plouffe scores.
Kendrys Morales reaches on a fielding error by first baseman Logan Morrison.   Brian Dozier scores.    Eduardo Nunez scores.    Trevor Plouffe to 3rd.    Kendrys Morales to 2nd.
Trevor Plouffe walks.   Eduardo Nunez to 2nd.
